# Context Pack Rule

Before implementation, create a Context Pack under `docs/context/` using `CONTEXT-PACK-TEMPLATE.md`.

Context Pack must define:

- Current TASK
- Related memory and docs
- Selected skills
- Subagent plan (if any)
- Files allowed to modify
- Files not allowed to modify
- Test commands
- Task boundary

Do not modify files outside the Context Pack without updating the Context Pack and TASK first.
